Elias","date":"August 1, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever forgets a prayer, let him pray it when he remembers. There is no expiation other than this.\u201d Then, the Prophet recited the verse, \"Perform prayer for My remembrance.\" (20:14) Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 597, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 684\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7927,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/11\/salah-as-you-see-me-praying\/","url_meta":{"origin":3947,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Pray as you see the Prophet praying","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 11, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Malik ibn al-Huwayrith reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Pray as you have seen me praying. When the time for prayer arrives, let one of you announce the call to prayer for everyone and then let the older of you lead the prayer.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":457,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/01\/27\/essentials-pillars-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":3947,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Islam: Essentials of salvation are pillars of Islam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 27, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported